name: DailyFantasyFootballPriceData
0:
”Alexa, open dfs data”
”Who is the most expensive player this week?”
”Who costs the most this week?”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: d. f. s. data
des: This skill, when prompted, will tell you who the most expensive player is right now for use with daily fantasy sports. It will tell you the player's name and their current salary.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
